  </div>


  <!-- News  -->
  <div>
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5 mt-10">📌 News</div>
  </div>
  <ul class="list-disc mx-6 mb-10 grid gap-2 text-lg">
    <li>
      <strong>[Jan 2026]</strong> Started an exchange program at <b>KTH Royal Institute of Technology</b>, Sweden 🇸🇪<br/>(Jan-Jun 2026)<span class="badge badge-secondary mx-2 font-bold">NEW</span>
    </li>
    <li><strong>[Dec 2025]</strong> Won the <b>Best Research Project Award (Grand Prize)</b> from POSTECH CSE</li>
    <li><strong>[Jun 2025]</strong> Honored to be selected for the <b>Presidential Science Scholarship</b>🏅</li>
  </ul>
  




